Jan 20 2004	Affordable Accomodations	With a Fitz's comp card you get reduced room rates, cash back and build up comp dollars to use for other purchases. Have stayed at most of the Downtown hotels, and The Fitz rates right up there, for the price. Andres, a sportsbook bartender is great. It's fun when you walk up to the bar and he remembers who you are from the last trip. If he tries to give you betting tips, bet the opposite. I have stayed there at least 10 times, and the only misfortune I had was, one time, only 2 of the 4 elevators, were operable for a day or so. I will continue to return, unless they quit honoring the comp card and it's benifits.	
